{"tid":2402931,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"要比壓力係比各業界  唔係比政府","createTime":"2021-02-10T18:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T02:36:43.000Z","uid":36807,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f295c6650d3585dd6ec234952ae55507211609f","tid":2402931,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:35:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">用安心出行APP 就儘量唔去幫襯 要表態</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好多野咁耐無做已經習慣咗唔做/搵到替代方式<br />\n做gym既唔去都一樣keep到身型<br />\n叫我睇戲要QR code入去 唔睇其實好小事<br />\n食野最多唔堂食 叫外賣 <br />\n<br />\n唔好去適應呢啲強制而不合理既事 <br />\n習慣咗盲目咗 你條底線只會越嚟越模糊<br />\n唔配合都係公民抗命<br />\n<br />\n等各業界出聲<br />\n依家係政府影響佢哋生意 搞到民怨四起 <br />\n無生意無飯開 唔係市民既錯<br />\n如果業界唔出聲到時攬炒更好 <br />\n同埋你會發現 好多野做少咗 真係慳咗好多錢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f0851465a6e13d2c66000e4c4544ce84df247b","tid":2402931,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"唔好中政府圈套<br />\n人民鬥人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac01f17767d5176af09c3dfdee2be48c9110a524","tid":2402931,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我整咗個安心出行翻版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2402888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2402888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好文欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbe153636d28a130fd942c78e000b6848fb03af","tid":2402931,"uid":167289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac01f17767d5176af09c3dfdee2be48c9110a524","tid":2402931,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我整咗個安心出行翻版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2402888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2402888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好文欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:40:5